@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_mbtnft(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = v1
    v0 = wp.abs(0.54)
    v1 = ((wp.abs(tmp + 0.61) * wp.abs(v2 + 0.98)) + (v0 - 0.02))
    v1 = (tmp - wp.exp(wp.sin(v1 + 0.49)))
    v1 = (wp.exp(0.52) + ((v0 + 0.78 / v1 + 0.10) + (tmp + 0.24 - tmp + 0.91)))
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.abs((v1 + 0.08 * v2 + 0.97)))
    v2 = 0.89
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.exp(v0))
    data[tid] = v0
